 {"id":"frankenjax-xjpu","title":"Harden BufferView slice range overflow","description":"Multi-pass bug hunt found crates/fj-runtime/src/buffer.rs BufferView::slice computes offset + len before validating bounds. For adversarial or saturated usize inputs this can panic in debug builds due integer overflow, and in optimized builds can wrap before the subsequent slice expression panics or misclassifies the range. Replace the addition with checked_add so out-of-range or overflowing slices return None as documented. Add a regression test using usize::MAX to prove BufferView::slice is panic-free and returns None for overflowing ranges. Validate with rch cargo test -p fj-runtime, rch cargo check -p fj-runtime --all-targets, rch cargo clippy -p fj-runtime --all-targets -- -D warnings, cargo fmt --check, and ubs on the touched file.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-28T20:28:47.354876805Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-28T20:31:59.713445908Z","closed_at":"2026-04-28T20:31:59.711609719Z","close_reason":"Hardened BufferView::slice with checked_add so overflowing offset+len returns None without panic; regression test covers usize::MAX overflow; workspace fmt/check/clippy/test pass on current HEAD.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
+{"id":"frankenjax-xozw","title":"ReduceWindow same padding is offset incorrectly","description":"eval_reduce_window computes SAME output length with ceil(input/stride) but starts every window at out_index * stride, so padding is effectively only on the high side. JAX/XLA SAME semantics split total padding with low padding floor(total/2), so examples like input [1,2,3,4,5], window=3, stride=1 should produce [3,6,9,12,9] instead of [6,9,12,9,5]. Implement low-padding offsets for SAME in rank-N reduce_window and add regression coverage.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-29T08:42:08.068354048Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-29T08:52:32.490134865Z","closed_at":"2026-04-29T08:52:32.487448832Z","close_reason":"Implemented centered SAME padding offsets for reduce_window and added rank-1/rank-2 regressions","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
